<mvc:View controllerName="UI5FioriForTools.controller.MainNavigation.Secondary.Product" 
	xmlns="sap.m" 
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
	xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form" busyIndicatorDelay="0">
	<Page
		id="productPage"
		title="Product Page"
		showNavButton="true"
		navButtonPress="onNavBack"
		class="sapUiResponsiveContentPadding">
		<content>
			<Panel
				id="productPanel"
				width="auto"
				class="sapUiNoContentPadding">
				<headerToolbar>
					<Toolbar>
						<Title text="{ProductName}" level="H2"/>
						<ToolbarSpacer />
					</Toolbar>
				</headerToolbar>
				<content>
					<f:SimpleForm
						editable="false"
						layout="ResponsiveGridLayout"
						labelSpanL="3" labelSpanM="3" emptySpanL="4" emptySpanM="4"
						columnsL="1" columnsM="1">
						<f:content>
							<Label text="Product Name" />
							<Text text="{ProductName}" />
							<Label text="Product ID" />
							<Text text="{ProductID}" />
							<Label text="Units in Stock" />
							<Text text="{UnitsInStock}" />
							<Label text="Units on Order" />
							<Text text="{UnitsOnOrder}" />
							<Label text="Unit Price" />
							<Text text="{UnitPrice}" />
							<Label text="Supplier ID" />
							<Text text="{SupplierID}" />
                            <Label text="Discontinued"/>
                            <Text text="{Discontinued}"/>
						</f:content>
					</f:SimpleForm>
				</content>
			</Panel>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>